<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lean-v">lean <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /liːn/    美 /liːn/  </p>
<p>(leant / leaned, leant / leaned)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>倾斜：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the Leaning Tower of Pisa 
比萨斜塔</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The column leans to the north. 
柱子向北倾斜。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(使) 倚靠；(使) 斜靠：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>lean against</strong> the wall 
倚在墙上</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The fence will break if you <strong>lean</strong> your weight <strong>on</strong> it. 
如果你靠在栅栏上，它会断的。</p></div></div>